  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00338', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-d1a761c9', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-02', NULL, 'essay', '食品安全衛生管理法第 5 條規定：「各級主管機關依科學實證，建立食品
